description:
Tell us which property/attribute of the "DarkBunny's" collection you found most fun.

To take the points you must answer with an attribute and its respective indicative number.
Example: Marital Status: Married /Number: DarkBunny #01

-If you have already participated in the previous Proof of Collector Stamp and have obtained your reward, you cannot obtain this award.
-Answers cannot be repeated.
name: Proof of Collector Stamp V2
